eNCA's Khayelihle Khumalo is in Johannesburg and Lethiwe Mdluli is in Durban to being you the latest. #eNCA Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Eskom will implement Stage 4 power cuts from 2pm until 10pm on Wednesday. The power utility says the blackouts are necessary after the loss of generation units at the Kusile and other power stations. Eskom says the probability of further power cuts remains high and they have urged all South Africans to reduce their use of electricity. #PowerAlert2
